NAME
	bug <message>

DESCRIPTION
	Send a message about a bug or misfunction you have run to to
	corresponding coder(s). The coder(s) have not to be in the game.

	USE THIS COMMAND A LOT! You should report EVERY TIME you spot a
	bug, since it will help making the game more enjoyable.

	If you report enough bugs, you might get rewarded.

SEE ALSO
	typo, idea
